\#\#\# Top Answer: You can open it with `\left.`, e.g.

```
\left. 
\begin{array}{c}
x\\
y
\end{array}
\right\rbrace = a

```

or,

```
\begin{equation}
\left\lbrace
\begin{array}{l}
\left. 
\begin{array}{c}
x\\
y
\end{array}
\right\rbrace = a\\
z = b
\end{array}
\right.
\end{equation}

```

